videos.description: Zach Brown drives and hits the pull-up jumper while getting fouled.
videos.headline: Brown makes jumper plus the foul

videos.description: South Dakota State uses some great passing to break the pass and set up a 3-pointer for Matt Daum.
videos.headline: SDSU's great passing leads to Daum 3-pointer

videos.description: Zach Brown uses the nice cut to get open and dunks it home for the Shockers.
videos.headline: Brown makes the great cut and slams it home

videos.description: Zach Brown makes the nice pass down to Shaquille Morris who scores down low.
videos.headline: Brown nice pass leads to Morris layup
